{"tid":1594910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[927愛丁堡 928金鐘 929銅鑼灣] 今日做了一張專用作 airdrop 的文宣","createTime":"2019-09-25T19:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:15:53.000Z","uid":200663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cedb4a8c36cd80d720169fd419c24a2bafa7ecc0","tid":1594910,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:58:28.000Z","msg":"今日開始用 airdrop 喺巴士 喺學校 喺吉野家 (<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) send 文宣<br />\n但如果 send 多過一張 而條友又唔收<br />\n咁佢祇會睇到預覧嗰一頁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今晚做咗張 時間表+罷食罷買+黑警罪行 合一嘅文宣<br />\n就算佢唔收 都會睇到呢三個資訊<br />\n唔知大家有咩意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LbcmDeT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbcmDeT.png&h=b9854ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我記得之前睇過有巴打做咗堆文宣<br />\n係一篇嘢兩三分鐘睇完 專係比人搭車睇嘅<br />\n唔知嗰位巴打堆文宣喺邊呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b73c7bb88c796c9c70e6d4b30d1087f86599441","tid":1594910,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:01:48.000Z","msg":"辛苦你，清晰易明，聽日會瘋狂AirDrop"},{"pid":"2cd28a2bcec19f10fe373bbe82eaf1897c7d35d6","tid":1594910,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b73c7bb88c796c9c70e6d4b30d1087f86599441","tid":1594910,"uid":310898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:01:48.000Z","msg":"辛苦你，清晰易明，聽日會瘋狂AirDrop"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:05:05.000Z","msg":"呢個 demo 嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過用嚟 airdrop 都得嘅<br />\n<br />\n原本想放篇文喺左手邊 但我未諗到 source <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有睇過牆紙 但佢好似吸淺黃多啲<br />\n想搵啲比淺藍睇嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ce19c62ca3771275de